    • MultiInterlinearProviderImpl

      public MultiInterlinearProviderImpl(String masterVersion, org.crosswire.jsword.versification.Versification masterVersification, String versions, String textScope, JSwordVersificationService versificationService, VocabularyService vocabProvider, boolean stripGreekAccents, boolean stripHebrewAccents, boolean stripVowels)
      sets up the interlinear provider with the correct version and text scope.
      Parameters:
      masterVersion - the master version
      versions - the versions to use to set up the interlinear
      textScope - the reference, or passage range that should be considered when setting up the interlinear provider
      versificationService - the service for working with a book
      vocabProvider - the provider of vocabulary
      stripGreekAccents - true to ensure Greek accents are stripped off Hebrew texts
      stripHebrewAccents - true to ensure Hebrew accents are stripped off Hebrew texts
      stripVowels - true to ensure accents are stripped off Greek texts
